<div class="wp-block-image">
<h1>Invitation to Collaborate:</h1>
<p>Please reach out to me, Allison A. Bay, rural health equity advocate, and public health professional in Atlanta, GA, at <em>abay1@student.gsu.edu</em>. You may visit my professional profile at<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/allison-bay-a06b00107/">&nbsp;Allison Bay | LinkedIn</a></p>
<p>I am interested in providing information to influencers and policymakers across the board-- Democrat, Republican, Independent, conservative, liberal... these labels do not matter when it comes to protecting the health and human rights of human beings in need of our support.&nbsp;</p>
<p>The following infographic contains information about improving health in rural GA, USA. Each region, state, and community have unique needs and, in many cases, differences in policies. A "one size fits all" approach will not work. Please contact me if you would like information about policies and strategies tailored to your needs.</p>
<figure class="aligncenter size-full"><img class="wp-image-27" src="https://allisonbay.edublogs.org/files/2022/04/ph-edu-policymakers.jpg" alt=""></figure>
</div>
